<s> (Barb) Your statement is correct - sort of.  </s>
<s> OIDs in ASN.1 define a de-codable structure that in turn, defines processing rules/semantics.  </s>
<s> In XML, you don't need an OID as a parse hint for the bytes that follow it because you can parse the XML directly.  </s>
<s> The important point is that the processing/semantic meaning for an XMLDSIG doc can change on the fly.  </s>
