<s> Actually I would avoid the construct for a quite different reason.  </s>
<s> OCSP responses are mainly constructed on an ad-hoc basis in response to an actual request.  </s>
<s> I don't see particular value in embedding ASN.1 structures of that type in XML documents.  </s>
<s> The OCSP server should have the manners to deliver the data in XML syntax.  </s>
